parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Smoke Emission from Dashboard Vents
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden emission of smoke from the dashboard vents can cause driver distraction, reduced visibility, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Smoke comes out of the dashboard vents
sudden appearance of smoke without warning
smoke is visible inside the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The use of an incorrect battery can lead to electrical system malfunctions, engine stalling, and potentially cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Battery does not match the manual specifications
electrical system malfunctions
engine stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Chafed Wiring and Ignition Coil Short Circuit
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The chafed wiring can cause a short circuit, leading to engine malfunction, stalling, or failure, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine malfunction
stalling
or failure
ignition coil short circuit
chafed wiring within the firewall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the tie rod can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The tie rod snaps or breaks while driving
the steering wheel delays returning to its normal position after making a turn
the vehicle pulls to one side while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A transmission fluid leak can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to stuck gears, loss of speed, and potential accidents.
symptoms: Transmission fluid leaking from underneath the hood
gears stuck
transmission slipping or hesitation
unusual noises or vibrations from the transmission.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission slipping or hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose speed, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Transmission jumps into neutral and back into gear
vehicle loses speed while driving
hesitation or slipping when shifting gears
unusual noises or vibrations from the transmission.
